text = "Left Click to Attack - Gain a burst of momentum towards your enemy!
~
Right Click to Defend - Parry at the moment of impact to defend yourself and repel your enemy!
~
When two cyclones meet, the slower of the two takes damage, and the faster regains some spin, which is like your health.
~
However, if you parry in time, the effect is reversed."
